{"tid":1461334,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣招募］青衣人站起來，加入青衣文宣！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:38:18.000Z","uid":199622,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd30b8e98680938265587b9f472a11d51d0c080d","tid":1461334,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"（代人出post)<br />\n<br />\n各位手足你好，我們是青衣文宣，主要專注於青衣的宣傳工作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=c0131081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我們是一群為了令運動繼續保留溫度而聚在一起的人，從而令政府不能逃避問責的責任。<br />\n<br />\n運動發展至今，政府仍未回應訴求，很多香港人都感到無力， 甚至憤怒。但我們已沒有退讓的餘地，沒有放棄的成本，只能有一起對準目標，因為政府有無數施政欺壓平民。<br />\n<br />\n如果你懷著相同理念，想出多一分力，行多一小步。 我們現在誠意邀請你加入我們。<br />\n<br />\n經過好多人幫手，開左兩次post 之後，我哋而已經開到3次傳單團，分別係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日<br />\n18號<br />\n21號</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果要keep住做更多嘅事，如banner or 放映會，就真係好需要人力幫手，所以我哋喺度想招募三種人才：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">活躍的天才</span></span><br />\n有心、發表建設性意見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">超級設計師</span></span><br />\n其實唔洗好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋好多人都係自學<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有經驗的老屎忽</span></span><br />\n因為小弟不才，無搞過放映會既經驗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=c0131081\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n其實青衣有好大個連儂牆（其實係橋先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） 仲有好多空間做到更加多嘅嘢，大家可以一齊發表下唔同睇法👀🧠 <br />\n<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;💻歡迎加入👩🏼&zwj;💻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=c0131081\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/Umuektn.jpg[/img[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmuektn.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=51997752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/Umuektn.jpg[/img[/img]</a>"},{"pid":"81c93fd5b1d7dbf60fd717c0b8879a37ec921821","tid":1461334,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:18:20.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"62734f388179623535b270501dce3a8d13f47884","tid":1461334,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:18:32.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"26b8abeaab836e2a08706da47f91315709216a0a","tid":1461334,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e8684d78a0952849fe82ea967fede348a26664df","tid":1461334,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"49dd42625aae56fec92b90aac047e40833